{
  "id": "transform-data",
  "title": "Transform data for better visualizations",
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "Transformations are a powerful way to manipulate data returned by a query before the system applies a visualization. Using transformations, you can:\n\n- Rename fields\n- Join time series/SQL-like data\n- Perform mathematical operations across queries\n- Use the output of one transformation as the input to another transformation\n\nIn this interactive guide, you'll set up a basic dashboard using the preinstalled Grafana data source and briefly explore the Transformations tab."
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "multistep",
          "content": "Click **New** in the top-right corner of the screen and select **New dashboard**.",
          "steps": [
            {
              "action": "highlight",
              "reftarget": "button[aria-label='New']"
            },
            {
              "action": "highlight",
              "reftarget": "a[href='/dashboard/new']"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "multistep",
          "content": "Click **Add visualization** and select the Grafana data source.",
          "steps": [
            {
              "action": "button",
              "reftarget": "button[data-testid='data-testid Create new panel button']"
            },
            {
              "action": "button",
              "reftarget": "-- Grafana --"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "button[data-testid='data-testid Tab All visualizations']",
          "content": "Click **All visualizations** to display the full list of visualization types."
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "div[data-testid='data-testid Plugin visualization item Time series']",
          "content": "Select **Time series**."
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "button[data-testid='data-testid RefreshPicker run button']",
          "content": "Click **Refresh** to visualize the data."
        }
      ],
      "id": "guide-section-34209",
      "title": "Set up a basic dashboard"
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "markdown",
          "content": "Great! You've set up a basic dashboard. Now let's check out transformations."
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "button[data-testid='data-testid Tab Transformations']",
          "content": "Below the panel, click the **Transformations** tab."
        },
        {
          "type": "markdown",
          "content": "Awesome! You've arrived at the Transformations tab. Here, you can choose from several options to improve how your data displays insights for you."
        },
        {
          "type": "multistep",
          "content": "To save space, not all of the available transformations are displayed initially. Scroll to the bottom of the tab and click **+ Show more** to open the **Add another transformation** drawer. \n\nThen select **Add field from calculation**.",
          "steps": [
            {
              "action": "highlight",
              "reftarget": "button[data-testid='data-testid add transformation button']"
            },
            {
              "action": "button",
              "reftarget": "Add field from calculation"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "markdown",
          "content": "The transformation has been added to your panel configuration. Let's review what else you can do in this tab. You can:"
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "hover",
          "reftarget": "button[data-testid='data-testid add transformation button']",
          "content": "Add another transformation.",
          "doIt": false
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "hover",
          "reftarget": "button[data-testid='data-testid remove all transformations button']",
          "content": "Delete all transformations.",
          "doIt": false
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "hover",
          "reftarget": "button[data-testid='data-testid Remove']",
          "content": "Or just delete this transformation.",
          "doIt": false
        },
        {
          "type": "multistep",
          "content": "Click **Filter** and choose which parts of the data the transformation applies to.",
          "steps": [
            {
              "action": "highlight",
              "reftarget": "button[data-testid='data-testid Filter']"
            },
            {
              "action": "formfill",
              "reftarget": "input:nth-of-type(1):nth-match(2)",
              "targetvalue": "Annotations"
            },
            {
              "action": "formfill",
              "reftarget": "input:nth-of-type(1):nth-match(2)",
              "targetvalue": "Query and Transformation"
            },
            {
              "action": "formfill",
              "reftarget": "input:nth-of-type(1):nth-match(3)",
              "targetvalue": "Query"
            },
            {
              "action": "highlight",
              "reftarget": "button[data-testid='data-testid Filter']"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "button[data-testid='data-testid Show transform help']",
          "content": "Click the information icon to see the documentation about how to use this transformation in a drawer."
        }
      ],
      "id": "guide-section-39958",
      "title": "Explore transformations"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "Congratulations! Now you know where to find several different options for transforming your data."
    }
  ],
